### Scenario 1: Scan Barcode "SKU123"

**BEFORE:**
```
Search: "SKU123"
Results (fuzzy matching, arbitrary order):
  1. SKU1234 (fuzzy - contains "SKU123")
  2. SKU123 (exact match - but appears later)
  3. SKU123-BLACK (fuzzy match)
