customer_id UUID (FK → customers.id)
total_amount INTEGER
created_at TIMESTAMP
...
```

### `sale_items` (Used for purchase details)
```sql
id UUID PRIMARY KEY
sale_id UUID (FK → sales.id)
quantity INTEGER
...
```

