### Step 3: Create Sale & Send STK Push
```typescript
// In payment handler:

// 1. Create sale with pending status
const sale = await createSale(
  branchId,
  cashierId,
  items,
  'mpesa',          // payment method
  customerId,
  cartDiscount,
  notes,
