## CHANGE 4: Redemption Ineligibility - Show Reason/Feedback

**File**: [components/pos/payment-panel.tsx](components/pos/payment-panel.tsx)

**Location**: Lines 500-564 (Redemption Section)

**Current Code**:
```typescript
